  "body": "When `helm install --atomic` encounters an error, any resources that already existed in the cluster and conflict with resources which would be created by `helm install` are deleted during rollback. The `--atomic` argument should allow existing resources to be left intact instead of deleting them.\r\n\r\nOutput of `helm version`:\r\n\r\n`version.BuildInfo{Version:\"v3.0+unreleased\", GitCommit:\"d285097f58818533bb20eb8dff1cfb0a88e1878f\", GitTreeState:\"clean\", GoVersion:\"go1.12.9\"}`",
